Author: medieval-spirit
Text: I don't know that this is a good idea for someone with an ED. In general when ppl guess weights they overestimate, but I think in your case the dysmorphia got in the way of objectivity and seeing yourself as you truly are. There's also Body Visualizer if you are really curious but it's not always realistic.
